org.edg.data.replication.optorsim

Class RandomWalkUnitaryAccessGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.edg.data.replication.optorsim.RandomWalkUnitaryAccessGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccessPatternGenerator

    public class RandomWalkUnitaryAccessGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
implements AccessPatternGenerator
    This class selects a file based on a unitary random walk. This means there is an equal chance of the next file being the previous one or the next one in the list of files in the GridJob. The starting point for the random walk is the same every time the same GridJob is run.

    Copyright (c) 2002 CERN, ITC-irst, PPARC, on behalf of the EU DataGrid. For license conditions see LICENSE file or http://www.edg.org/license.html
